Introducing a productivity tool for GitHub users - StarWall chrome extension allows you to easily search through all of your starred repositories, as well as the starred repositories of the users you follow. 

With this powerful extension, you'll never have to waste time scrolling through your GitHub dashboard again - simply type in a keyword or phrase, and our extension will quickly find the repository you're looking for. 

Many of us have hundreds of starred repositories and it can be overwhelming to find the one you need, but with our extension, you can easily find the repository you need, even if you've forgotten about it. 

Additionally, the extension allows you to discover interesting repositories starred by the people you follow. 
Whether you're a developer, a designer, or just a casual GitHub user, this extension is an essential tool for staying organized and on top of your work.

StarWall source code: https://github.com/iRay/StarWall
